abstract: The search giant faced new accusations that it was blocking a smaller European service from competing.
snippet: The search giant faced new accusations that it was blocking a smaller European service from competing.
lead_paragraph: BRUSSELS  Google faced new accusations on Tuesday that it was blocking a smaller European search service by restricting the use of its powerful system for attracting advertisers.

headline.main: Google Faces New Antitrust Charges in Europe
headline.print_headline: New Complaint Against Google From a French Search Service
